What you need to know:  At a junior golfers event last Sunday, Njoroge Kibugu was visibly uncomfortable about being flocked by young golfers seeking to know how he excelledThe soft spoken lad, who wears a golden afro hairstyle, stole the show by stunning all the local professionals to finish 64 out of 144 golfers who entered the competition and top in the amateur sectionThe golf protégé reckons that his impressive performance and the short stint with President Kenyatta during the ceremony give him every reason to be proud of his journey thus far